	<h1 class="title">「日本語」日本人说的&quot;御节料理&quot;，其实就是年夜饭啦</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/147/small/147.jpg?1418116339" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">陈思吟 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-12 07:30:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/18950/medium/18950.jpg?1449828448" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


